components.name: ButtonComponent
components.templateData:
<button
	class="button"
	(click)="emitClick()"
	[ngClass]="{
		'button--main': type === 'main',
		'button--main--disabled': type === 'main' && disabled,
		'button--success': type === 'success',
		'button--success--disabled': type === 'success' && disabled,
		'button--outline-main': type === 'outline-main',
		'button--outline-main--disabled': type === 'outline-main' && disabled,
		'button--outline-success': type === 'outline-success',
		'button--outline-success--disabled': type === 'outline-success' && disabled,
		'button--white': type === 'white',
		'button--white--disabled': type === 'white' && disabled,
		'button--black': type === 'black',
		'button--black--disabled': type === 'black' && disabled,
		'button--small': small
	}"
	[style]="customStyles"
>
	{{ text }}
</button>

components.sourceCode:
import { Component, Input } from '@angular/core';
import { SafeHtml } from '@angular/platform-browser';
import { CountryBadgeService } from './country-badge.service';

@Component({
	selector: 'tg-country-badge',
	templateUrl: './country-badge.component.html',
	styleUrls: ['./country-badge.component.scss']
})
export class CountryBadgeComponent {

	/**
	 * Sets the size of the badge
	 */
	@Input() size: number = 14;

	/**
	 * Injects the dependencies
	 * 
	 * @param countryBadgeService Service for badges of countries
	 */
	constructor(private countryBadgeService: CountryBadgeService) {}

	/**
	 * Sets the name of the country
	 * It can be:
	 * 
	 * - south-africa
	 * - germany
	 * - argentina
	 * - australia
	 * - austria
	 * - belgium
	 * - bolivia
	 * - brazil
	 * - bulgaria
	 * - canada
	 * - chile
	 * - china
	 * - colombia
	 * - south-koreia
	 * - croatia
	 * - denmark
	 * - emirates
	 * - scotia
	 * - slovenia
	 * - spain
	 * - spain
	 * - finland
	 * - france
	 * - georgia
	 * - greece
	 * - netherlands
	 * - hungary
	 * - india
	 * - indonesia
	 * - england
	 * - ireland
	 * - israel
	 * - italy
	 * - jamaica
	 * - japan
	 * - lebanon
	 * - malta
	 * - marocco
	 * - mexico
	 * - norway
	 * - new-zeland
	 * - peru
	 * - poland
	 * - portugal
	 * - czech-republic
	 * - romania
	 * - russia
	 * - serbia-and-montenegro
	 * - sweden
	 * - switzerland
	 * - tunisia
	 * - turkey
	 * - ukraine
	 * - uruguay
	 * - usa
	 * - venezuela
	 */
	@Input() country: string;

	/**
	 * Gets the badge from the service
	 * 
	 * @returns {SafeHtml} SVG of the badge
	 */
	get badge(): SafeHtml {
		return this.countryBadgeService.getBadge(this.country, this.size);
	}
}
